Auto convertion for files into PDF format and merge them into one giant pdf file!
The following are the usage of the merge.go program

go run merge.go output.pdf input1.pdf input2.pdf ...

go run merge.go -- executive command
output.pdf      -- path and name of the output pdf file
input1.pdf      -- path and name of the first pdf file to be merged
input2.pdf           -- path and name of the second pdf file to be merged
...                  -- as many input pdf file as possible
If the input file is not pdf, as long as it is DOC, DOCX, PNG, JPEG, GIF, JPG, TXT, HTML, merge.go will convert them to pdf for you
